00:58:55,110 --> 00:58:56,210
<font color="yellow">...dia pasti...</font>

953
00:58:56,710 --> 00:58:58,680
<font color="yellow">...menggila lagi.</font>

954
00:58:59,550 --> 00:59:02,950
<font color="yellow">Yang bisa kupikirkan...</font>

955
00:59:03,750 --> 00:59:05,080
<font color="yellow">...hanyalah anakku sendiri.</font>

956
00:59:06,280 --> 00:59:07,280
<font color="yellow">Maaf.</font>

957
00:59:08,450 --> 00:59:09,450
<font color="yellow">Maafkan aku.</font>

958
00:59:11,410 --> 00:59:12,850
<font color="yellow">Teganya dirimu?</font>

959
00:59:14,380 --> 00:59:16,750
<font color="yellow">Melihat orang merendahkanku...</font>

960
00:59:20,110 --> 00:59:21,210
<font color="yellow">...tidak sesulit...</font>

961
00:59:21,850 --> 00:59:23,280
<font color="yellow">...aku membencinya...</font>

962
00:59:23,950 --> 00:59:25,250
<font color="yellow">...setiap waktu.</font>

963
00:59:26,410 --> 00:59:28,280
<font color="yellow">Teganya kau melakukan ini padaku?</font>

964
00:59:33,710 --> 00:59:34,710
<font color="yellow">Ini...</font>

965
00:59:35,210 --> 00:59:36,450
<font color="yellow">...semua salahku.</font>

966
00:59:37,280 --> 00:59:38,380
<font color="yellow">Aku salah.</font>

967
00:59:40,110 --> 00:59:41,810
<font color="yellow">Jangan maafkan...</font>

968
00:59:44,510 --> 00:59:46,210
<font color="yellow">...wanita tua ini.</font>

969
00:59:47,680 --> 00:59:49,210
<font color="yellow">Tapi, maafkanlah...</font>

970
00:59:52,250 --> 00:59:53,750
<font color="yellow">...anakku.</font>

971
01:00:16,210 --> 01:00:17,210
<font color="yellow">Aku kemari...</font>

972
01:00:17,810 --> 01:00:19,950
<font color="yellow">...karena ibuku tidak ada di rumah.</font>

973
01:00:20,950 --> 01:00:21,980
<font color="yellow">Apa kebetulan dia kemari?</font>

974
01:00:23,410 --> 01:00:24,580
<font color="yellow">Aku tahu tidak sopan...</font>

975
01:00:25,210 --> 01:00:26,510
<font color="yellow">...bertamu malam-malam begini.</font>

976
01:00:28,080 --> 01:00:30,880
<font color="yellow">Aku terus saja mengganggumu...,</font>

977
01:00:31,780 --> 01:00:33,410
<font color="yellow">...tapi bagaimana lagi...</font>

978
01:00:34,210 --> 01:00:35,650
<font color="yellow">...ini situasi yang mendesak.</font>

979
01:00:37,550 --> 01:00:38,550
<font color="yellow">Apa ibuku...</font>

980
01:00:39,280 --> 01:00:40,350
<font color="yellow">...ada disini?</font>

981
01:00:53,850 --> 01:00:54,850
<font color="yellow">Baek Hee.</font>

982
01:00:56,250 --> 01:00:57,350
<font color="yellow">Ada apa?</font>

983
01:00:58,280 --> 01:00:59,380
<font color="yellow">Kenapa menangis?</font>

984
01:01:00,180 --> 01:01:01,910
<font color="yellow">Apa ada yang membuatmu marah?</font>

985
01:01:02,710 --> 01:01:03,850
<font color="yellow">Kalau ada, kenapa?</font>

986
01:01:05,680 --> 01:01:07,080
<font color="yellow">Kau akan memukulinya seperti dulu?</font>

987
01:01:07,980 --> 01:01:10,610
<font color="yellow">Katakan padaku apa yang
membuatmu kesal.</font>

988
01:01:11,510 --> 01:01:12,610
<font color="yellow">Kau.</font>

989
01:01:14,280 --> 01:01:16,810
<font color="yellow">Aku marah karena kau, idiot.</font>

990
01:01:18,710 --> 01:01:19,880
<font color="yellow">Kenapa kau tak bisa berhenti menggangguku?</font>

991
01:01:21,180 --> 01:01:22,850
<font color="yellow">Kenapa kau terus menggangguku?</font>

992
01:01:26,180 --> 01:01:28,350
<font color="yellow">Baiklah. Aku mengerti.</font>

993
01:01:28,980 --> 01:01:32,310
<font color="yellow">Aku akan pindah atau apalah supaya
kau tidak perlu melihatku lagi.</font>

994
01:01:33,180 --> 01:01:34,810
<font color="yellow">Maaf atas semuanya.</font>

995
01:01:35,450 --> 01:01:38,310
<font color="yellow">Minta maaf apa?</font>

996
01:01:39,480 --> 01:01:41,080
<font color="yellow">Kenapa minta maaf?</font>

997
01:01:44,150 --> 01:01:45,880
<font color="yellow">Kenapa kau minta maaf?</font>

998
01:01:47,650 --> 01:01:50,080
<font color="yellow">Kenapa kau minta maaf
seperti orang bodoh?</font>

999
01:02:11,950 --> 01:02:13,010
<font color="yellow">Yang Baek Hee.</font>

1000
01:02:15,350 --> 01:02:17,010
<font color="yellow">Jangan menangis.</font>

1001
01:02:18,710 --> 01:02:21,080
<font color="yellow">Berhenti menangis dan dengarlah.</font>

1002
01:02:22,280 --> 01:02:23,410
<font color="yellow">Kau hanya perlu...</font>

1003
01:02:24,410 --> 01:02:25,750
<font color="yellow">...melihat ke depan dan terus maju.</font>

1004
01:02:28,150 --> 01:02:30,610
<font color="yellow">Jangan berpaling ke masa lalu.</font>

1005
01:02:32,080 --> 01:02:33,480
<font color="yellow">Lihat saja ke depan...</font>

1006
01:02:35,180 --> 01:02:36,980
<font color="yellow">...dan terus maju.</font>

1007
01:02:39,680 --> 01:02:41,310
<font color="yellow">Kita menghabiskan 18 tahun
tumbuh bersama.</font>

1008
01:02:43,080 --> 01:02:44,750
<font color="yellow">Dan selama 18 tahun terakhir,
aku benci kau.</font>

1009
01:02:47,350 --> 01:02:48,510
<font color="yellow">Apa yang harus kulakukan?</font>

1010
01:02:49,380 --> 01:02:50,850
<font color="yellow">Apa yang harus kulakukan sekarang?</font>

1011
01:02:52,750 --> 01:02:53,950
<font color="yellow">Katakanlah sesuatu.</font>

1012
01:02:54,410 --> 01:02:56,650
<font color="yellow">Apa yang akan kulakukan sekarang?</font>

